A-thumb.jpg",{"image":130,"thumb":276,"title":123},"ISic001677_B_tiled-thumb.tif",{"image":278,"thumb":279,"title":123},"ISic001677_B.jpg","ISic001677_B-thumb.jpg",{"image":120,"thumb":266,"title":135},{"image":268,"thumb":269,"title":135},[283],{"html":56},"\u003C?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n\u003C?xml-model href=\"https://epidoc.stoa.org/schema/latest/tei-epidoc.rng\" type=\"application/xml\" schematypens=\"http://relaxng.org/ns/structure/1.0\"?>\n\u003C?xml-model href=\"../schematron/ircyr-checking.sch\" schematypens=\"http://purl.oclc.org/dsdl/schematron\"?>\n\u003CTEI xmlns=\"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0\" xmlns:xi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude\" xml:lang=\"en\">\n    \u003CteiHeader>\n        \u003CfileDesc>\n            \u003CtitleStmt>\n                \u003Ctitle>Theatre seat inscription\u003C/title>\n                \u003Ceditor ref=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/editor>\n                \u003Cprincipal ref=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/principal>\n                \u003Cfunder>John Fell OUP Research Fund\u003C/funder>\n                \u003Cfunder>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://cordis.europa.eu/project/id/885040\">ERC Advanced Grant no.885040\u003C/ref>\n                \u003C/funder>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"JP\" ref=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Cresp>original data collection and editing\u003C/resp>\n                \u003C/respStmt>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"JCu\" ref=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0002-6686-3728\">James Cummings\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Cresp>establishment of EpiDoc template\u003C/resp>\n                \u003C/respStmt>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"SS\" ref=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3914-9569\">Simona Stoyanova\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Cresp>standardisation of template and tidying up encoding\u003C/resp>\n                \u003C/respStmt>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"MMohr\"/>\n                    \u003Cresp>provision of data and images\u003C/resp>\n                \u003C/respStmt>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"RC\" ref=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0002-0100-7437\">Robert Crellin\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Cresp>lemmatization and linguistic analysis\u003C/resp>\n                \u003C/respStmt>\n            \u003CrespStmt>\u003Cname xml:id=\"Coccato\" ref=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0002-6641-2820\">Alessia Coccato\u003C/name>\u003Cresp>Petrographic observation and analysis\u003C/resp>\u003C/respStmt>\n            \u003C/titleStmt>\n            \u003CpublicationStmt>\n                \u003Cauthority>I.Sicily\u003C/authority>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"filename\">ISic001677\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"TM\"/>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"EDR\"/>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"EDH\"/>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"EDCS\"/>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"PHI\"/>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"URI\">http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001677\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cavailability>\n                    \u003Clicence target=\"http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/\">Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence\u003C/licence>\n                \u003C/availability>\n            \u003C/publicationStmt>\n            \u003CsourceDesc>\n                \u003CmsDesc>\n                    \u003CmsIdentifier>\n                        \u003Ccountry>Italy\u003C/country>\n                        \u003Cregion>Sicily\u003C/region>\n                        \u003Csettlement>San Cipirello\u003C/settlement>\n                        \u003Crepository role=\"site\" ref=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/museum/193\">Area archeologica del Monte Iato\u003C/repository>\n                        \u003Cidno type=\"inventory\"/>\n                        \u003C!--Adding location for old id numbers if available-->\n                        \u003CaltIdentifier>\n                            \u003Csettlement/>\n                            \u003Crepository/>\n                            \u003Cidno type=\"old\"/>\n                        \u003C/altIdentifier>\n                    \u003C/msIdentifier>\n                    \u003CmsContents>\n                        \u003CtextLang mainLang=\"grc\">Ancient Greek\u003C/textLang>\n                    \u003C/msContents>\n                    \u003CphysDesc>\n                        \u003CobjectDesc>\n                            \u003CsupportDesc>\n                                \u003Csupport>\n                                    \u003Cp/>\n                                    \u003Cmaterial ana=\"#material.inorganic.stone\" type=\"stone.unspecified\" subtype=\"unspecified\" resp=\"#Coccato\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/66.html\">limestone\u003C/material>\n                                    \u003CobjectType ana=\"#object.seat\" ref=\"https://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/226.html\">seat\u003C/objectType>\n                                    \u003Cdimensions>\u003C!-- not recorded-->\n                                        \u003Cheight unit=\"cm\"/>\n                                        \u003Cwidth unit=\"cm\"/>\n                                        \u003Cdepth unit=\"cm\"/>\n                                    \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003C/support>\n                                \u003Ccondition ana=\"#condition.complete\"/>\n                            \u003C/supportDesc>\n                            \u003ClayoutDesc>\n                                \u003Clayout>\n                                    \u003Cp>The same two letters are repeated in large form on the upper surface of the seat, and in monogrammatic form on the front vertical face of the same slab\u003C/p>\n                                    \u003Crs ana=\"#execution.chiselled\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/1\">chiselled\u003C/rs>\n                                    \u003Cdamage ana=\"#text_condition.complete\"/>\n                                \u003C/layout>\n                            \u003C/layoutDesc>\n                        \u003C/objectDesc>\n                        \u003ChandDesc>\n                            \u003ChandNote>\n                                \u003Cp>Large plain letters without serifs on the flat surface, smaller but similar on the vertical face; alpha is broad with a straight bar; pi has verticals of equal length and there is no extension of the horizontal beyond the verticals.\u003C/p>\n                                \u003Cp>\n                                    Types list:\n                                    \u003Cref target=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type1.html\">Α type1\u003C/ref>\n                                    \u003Cref target=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type1.3.html\">Α type1.3\u003C/ref>\n                                    \u003Cref target=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Π-type1.html\">Π type1\u003C/ref>\n                                    \u003Cref target=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Π-type1.1.html\">Π type1.1\u003C/ref>\n                                    \u003Cref target=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Π-type2.html\">Π type2\u003C/ref>\n                                    \u003Cref target=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Π-type2.1.html\">Π type2.1\u003C/ref>\n                                \u003C/p>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line1\" to=\"line1\">Line 1\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"letterHeight\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\"/>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                            \u003C/handNote>\n                        \u003C/handDesc>\n                    \u003C/physDesc>\n                    \u003Chistory>\n                        \u003Corigin>\n                            \u003CorigPlace>\u003Cregion>Sicilia\u003C/region>\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"ancient\" ref=\"http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462258\" corresp=\"#findspot\">Ietas\u003C/placeName>\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"modern\" ref=\"http://sws.geonames.org/2524540\">Monte Iato\u003C/placeName>\n                                \u003Cgeo>37.967050, 13.198199\u003C/geo>\n                            \u003C/origPlace>\n                            \u003CorigDate datingMethod=\"#julian\" notBefore-custom=\"-0220\" notAfter-custom=\"-0180\" evidence=\"archaeological-context\">The monumental phase of the theatre, including the seats, is probably to be dated around 200 BCE (M. Mohr)\u003C/origDate>\n                        \u003C/origin>\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"found\" subtype=\"discovered\" when=\"1986\" xml:id=\"findspot\">Identified on a preserved seat of the theatre during the excavations of 1986\u003Cgeo>37.967621, 13.197898\u003C/geo>\u003C/provenance>\u003C!-- geo for front centre of seating in theatre; precise geo coordinates not yet identified -->\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"observed\" corresp=\"#findspot\">in situ\u003C/provenance>\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"observed\" subtype=\"autopsied\">None\u003C/provenance>\n                        \u003Cacquisition/>\n                    \u003C/history>\n                \u003C/msDesc>\n            \u003C/sourceDesc>\n        \u003C/fileDesc>\n        \u003CencodingDesc>\n            \u003Cp>Encoded following EpiDoc guidelines 9.2\u003C/p>\n            \u003Cxi:include href=\"../alists/ISicily-taxonomies.xml\">\n                \u003Cxi:fallback>\n                    \u003Cp>Taxonomies for ISicily controlled values\u003C/p>\n                \u003C/xi:fallback>\n            \u003C/xi:include>\n            \u003Cxi:include href=\"../alists/charDecl.xml\">\n                \u003Cxi:fallback>\n                    \u003Cp>ISicily glyphs authority list\u003C/p>\n                \u003C/xi:fallback>\n            \u003C/xi:include>\n        \u003C/encodingDesc>\n        \u003CprofileDesc>\n            \u003CcalendarDesc>\n                \u003Ccalendar xml:id=\"julian\">\n                    \u003Cp>Julian Calendar\u003C/p>\n                \u003C/calendar>\n            \u003C/calendarDesc>\n            \u003ClangUsage>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"en\">English\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"it\">Italian\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"grc\">Ancient Greek\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"la\">Latin\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"he\">Hebrew\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"phn\">Phoenician\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"xpu\">Punic\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"osc\">Oscan\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"xly\">Elymian\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"scx\">Sikel\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"sxc\">Sikan\u003C/language>\n            \u003C/langUsage>\n            \u003CtextClass>\n                \u003Ckeywords scheme=\"https://ontology.inscriptiones.org/type_of_inscription\">\n                    \u003Cterm ana=\"#function.seat\" ref=\"https://ontology.inscriptiones.org/type_of_inscription/Seat_inscription\">seat inscription\u003C/term>\n                \u003C/keywords>\n            \u003C/textClass>\n        \u003C/profileDesc>\n        \u003CrevisionDesc status=\"draft\">\n            \u003ClistChange>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2021-05-20\" who=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag created file from template based upon publication and information/photographs provided by M. Mohr\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2025-10-15\" who=\"#RC\">Robert Crellin added local IDs to edition elements\u003C/change>\n            \u003C/listChange>\n        \u003C/revisionDesc>\n    \u003C/teiHeader>\n    \u003Cfacsimile>\n        \u003Csurface type=\"front\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic001677_tiled.tif\" height=\"3340px\" width=\"5110px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>Photo courtesy Zurich Ietas excavations\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic001677.jpg\" height=\"3340px\" width=\"5110px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>Photo courtesy Zurich Ietas excavations\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic001677_A_tiled.tif\" height=\"3377px\" width=\"5160px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>Photo courtesy Zurich Ietas excavations\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic001677_A.jpg\" height=\"3377px\" width=\"5160px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>Photo courtesy Zurich Ietas excavations\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic001677_B_tiled.tif\" height=\"3452px\" width=\"5110px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>Photo courtesy Zurich Ietas excavations\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic001677_B.jpg\" height=\"3452px\" width=\"5110px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>Photo courtesy Zurich Ietas excavations\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n        \u003C/surface>\n        \u003Csurface type=\"front\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic001677_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic001677.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n        \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"grc\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003Cdiv type=\"textpart\" subtype=\"section\" n=\"A\">\n                    \u003Cab>\n                        \u003Clb n=\"1\" xml:id=\"BΠΤAK\"/>\u003Corig xml:id=\"BΠΤAU\" n=\"5\">ΑΠ\u003C/orig>\n                    \u003C/ab>\n                \u003C/div>\n                \u003Cdiv type=\"textpart\" subtype=\"section\" n=\"B\">\n                    \u003Cab>\n                        \u003Clb n=\"1\" xml:id=\"BΠΤAe\"/>\u003Corig xml:id=\"BΠΤAo\" n=\"10\">\u003Chi rend=\"small\" xml:id=\"BΠΤAy\">Α\u003C/hi>\u003Chi rend=\"stacked\" xml:id=\"BΠΤAΙ\">Π\u003C/hi>\u003C/orig>\n                    \u003C/ab>\n                \u003C/div>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\n                    \u003Capp>\n                        \u003Cnote>Text from photographs\u003C/note>\n                    \u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\">\n                \u003Cp/>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003Cp>In detailed study of the theatre in 1986 this was the only inscription identified on the preserved seats. It is a reasonable assumption that since the same pair of letters is repeated, they have the same reference. The text on the vertical face of the seat (text B) is presented in the form of a monogram, with alpha much smaller and placed within the pi. The implication of the larger letters set out on the horizontal surface (text A) is that the small alpha should be read first in resolving such a monogrammatic presentation.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Isler\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1986\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>29-30 with fig. 3\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/N52H9DRN\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001915\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001915\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n\t       \u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
